---
title: Smart Moo Shu-Sesame Beef Patties with Crisp Salad and Tahini-Drizzle
description: Lightly sweetened, deeply savoury and bolstered by the sweetness of grated apple as well as a zippy Moo Shu Spice Blend, these beef patties will be enjoyed by everyone in your family.

